## 链栈

关于链栈，其实现方法和单链表非常类似，链栈本就是一种特殊的单链表，和普通单链表不同的是，链栈的插入和删除只能在栈顶进行。我们假设在有头结点的前提下先实现了一下，发现链栈可以使用头插法来创建栈，入栈时只需要对头结点一直实行**后插操作**，出栈时需要删除**头结点后面的结点**。

#### 建栈

```c
typedef struct StackNode{
    int data;
    struct StackNode *next;
}StackNode,*LinkStackptr;
```

#### 初始化

```c
int InitStack(LinkStackptr &L){
    L = (StackNode*) malloc(sizeof (StackNode *));
    L->next = NULL;//创建头结点，并初始化为空链表
}
```

#### 头插

```c
int HeadPush(LinkStackptr &L){
    int x;
    L = (StackNode*) malloc(sizeof (StackNode*));
    L->next = NULL;
    StackNode *s;
    scanf("%d",&x);
    while(x!=999){
        s = (StackNode*) malloc(sizeof (StackNode*));
        s->data = x;
        s->next = L->next;
        L->next = s;
        scanf("%d",&x);
    }
    return OK;
}
```

#### 入栈

```c
int push(LinkStackptr &L,int e){
    StackNode *s;
    s = (StackNode*) malloc(sizeof (StackNode*));
    s->data = e;
    s->next = L->next;
    L->next = s;
    return OK;
}
```

#### 出栈

```c
int pop(LinkStackptr &L,int *e) {
    if (L->next == NULL) {
        return ERROR;
    }
    StackNode *s = L->next;
    *e = s->data;
    L->next = s->next;
    free(s);
    return OK;
}
```

#### 主函数及运行截图

```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
#include "L.h"

int main (){
    LinkStackptr L;
    int e;
    HeadPush(L);
    push(L,4);
    pop(L,&e);
    Print(L);
    return 0;
}
```

